'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #1873] on 26 February 2000 at 7:12:14 pm'!"Change Set:		12UncatchableHalt-smaDate:			12 February 2000Author:			Stefan Matthias AustThis is my proposal for an uncatchable halt, that is  [self halt] on: Error do: []will not silently do nothing but still open a debug notifier.On the other hand,  [self halt] on: Halt do: []will catch the halt."!!Exception class methodsFor: 'exceptionSelector' stamp: 'sma 2/12/2000 14:15'!handles: exception	"Determine whether an exception handler will accept a signaled exception."	(exception isKindOf: Halt) ifTrue: [^ false].	^ exception isKindOf: self! !!Halt class methodsFor: 'exceptionSelector' stamp: 'sma 2/26/2000 18:11'!handles: exception	"Determine whether an exception handler will accept a signaled exception."	^ exception isKindOf: self! !